caption: A lovely fountain in a small square, there a many similar to this square scattered all over paris, however this one has become incredibly popular as it is also home to the apartment building, that has been made famous in the TV series Emily in Paris.
I honestly like this small garden in front of the famous emily in paris building. It’s serene even with all the tourists, and a nice place to take a small break and enjoy the surroundings

It's a quiet little square in the area between the Pantheon and the Luxembourg Gardens. Before the screening of the series "Emily in Paris" almost no one knew the square and even if you passed by you would certainly not stop for pictures. Now, it belongs to the attractions of Paris if you are a fan of the "Emily in Paris" series, and fortunately it remains a quiet square that gathers a large number of tourists for pictures.
